Interface AvailabilitySet

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface AvailabilitySet
extends GroupableResource, Refreshable<AvailabilitySet>, Wrapper<AvailabilitySetInner>, Updatable<AvailabilitySet.Update>

      • updateDomainCount

        int updateDomainCount()
        Returns the update domain count of an availability set.

        An update domain represents the group of virtual machines and underlying physical hardware that can be rebooted at the same time.

        Returns:
        the update domain count

      • faultDomainCount
